{"tid":470543,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都鍾意睇安達充？","createTime":"2017-11-16T11:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T03:37:07.000Z","uid":96308,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3715f9b39e29e37162b9c8ca16df9a1a41a327","tid":470543,"uid":96308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣都好鍾意安達充嘅漫畫/動畫?<br />\n每一本都可以睇好多次，而且次次睇都會領悟到唔同意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熱血位睇親都起哂雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189eaa0187c4175b5f5e420a01840aca84479cb6","tid":470543,"uid":84588,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:45:40.000Z","msg":"cross game"},{"pid":"aeb1e4c2afcdd262f5362eaebb97dd98261dd7e7","tid":470543,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:46:41.000Z","msg":"青葉"},{"pid":"ffb4536b1497ee948885cb839e123a6eef475226","tid":470543,"uid":96308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"如果cross game若葉冇死就好，淨係出過場一集，不過我已經好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0442b4512b14c4d8b0d8ffb8ff520b56412972","tid":470543,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果cross game若葉冇死就好，淨係出過場一集，不過我已經好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當絢香一唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ba889b8460862f264a93a734d585df5633ae28","tid":470543,"uid":37757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果cross game若葉冇死就好，淨係出過場一集，不過我已經好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當絢香一唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSUMMER RAIN <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9af3286415829ba3672a5016bdc4ce579d0882","tid":470543,"uid":96308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:52:06.000Z","msg":"不過論女主角都係淺倉南最正，無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d6ef0023515d258ba1c595eca41ef8355a8ea8","tid":470543,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果cross game若葉冇死就好，淨係出過場一集，不過我已經好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n若葉因為好照顧光仔所以一開始都鐘意, <br />\n但睇落去最後光仔大左, 最夾既反而係青葉"},{"pid":"fe95802d510b63d07284e82a319b0b1245464677","tid":470543,"uid":96308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果cross game若葉冇死就好，淨係出過場一集，不過我已經好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n若葉因為好照顧光仔所以一開始都鐘意, <br />\n但睇落去最後光仔大左, 最夾既反而係青葉</blockquote><br />\n因為光仔大個左慢慢似左若葉，所以先夾左。"},{"pid":"bd4edf98e7c48cdb5ee73f831ec1c6c10f53fb71","tid":470543,"uid":4955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"睇過touch 正"},{"pid":"8101d5eb4bd561512e23c0bca4d4472d81884d13","tid":470543,"uid":59465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"最屈機係啲分鏡<br />\n唔使寫對白<br />\n就咁睇畫面<br />\n個故事/意景都表達到出嚟<br />\n<br />\n又成日自己抽自己水 <br />\n真心欣賞"},{"pid":"399ca2832c37ce086602dfd4bd26d902bf19f57c","tid":470543,"uid":4955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"岩先查返原來touch有續集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361ec5264d7085a5ee62c82dc1e0bf19692c2681","tid":470543,"uid":5297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"Touch, H2"},{"pid":"16ec8a6